## Frontend -> Backend API base URL (optional)
#
# - If not set, frontend will call same-origin `/api/*` endpoints.
# - In local dev, Vite proxy already forwards `/api/*` to `http://127.0.0.1:8000`.
# - If you deploy frontend and backend on different origins, set this to your backend base URL.
#
# Example:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000

